Roadmap

  • January 2017

    BitCashGold project is Stated and discussed based on the need to solve one of the mayor problems in most of the people: get and be part of a truly economic system that allows not only to change for good that reality but also, with the great expectation of creating a strong foundation worldwide that really change millions of lives around the world.

  • August 2017

    BitCashGold is patented and moving forward to stablish its vision by creating a real human value adding important assets like “the art of managing money”, “financial education”, “Personal growth”, “money education”, “the art of being happy”, doing join ventures with recognized corporations pioneer in those areas.

  • February 2018

    BitCashGold develops its corporate image including commercial strategies sales and growth projection. Also, BitCashGold releases its master Eco-System plan that guaranties the enormous potential and strong growth of the community (all aspects detailed on whitepaper)

  • March 2018

    BitCashGold develops all the general programming infrastructure that includes all related to customer experience, system core, multiple validating tests.

  • April 2018


    The development of the BitCashGold tokens begins



  • August 2018

    ICO released! Starts on November 1st up to December 31st




  • January 2019


    Manufacture and delivery of BitCashGold Tokens




  • March 2019


    Availability of BitCashGold in Exchanges (March 28th) and coinmarketcap.com




  • April 2019


    April 15th onwards, aggressive expansion of BitCashGold worldwide Starting in Latin America and then Europe.
